    public interface SpecializableTerm
extends Term, VocabularyStatement
    A representation of the model object 'Specializable Term'. SpecializableTerm is a term that can specialized in a taxonomy. It can have zero or more specializations.

    The following features are supported:

    • Owned Specializations
